the place to start your monk collection a great remastered version of one of monks ' masterpiece recordings . every selection here offers something unexpected and the entire cd swings like crazy . monks comping on the title track criss cross behind charlie rouses 's temor is something to behold . he is never where you think he 's going and yet melodic and perfectly in the tune . this guy was really something special and this cd offers a chance to hear him at his peak . buy it..you ca n't go wrong here